1 (c) Notwithstanding section 480-2 or any other law to the
2 contrary, no person may bring a private action to enforce this
3 section.
4 (d) Any person who engages in cash transaction rounding
5 pursuant to this section shall not be subject to section
6 486-116.
7 (e) For the purposes of this section, "total transaction
8 amount" includes fees, surcharges, and taxes."
9 SECTION 3. This Act does not affect rights and duties that
10 matured, penalties that were incurred, and proceedings that were
11 begun before its effective date.
12 SECTION 4. New statutory material is underscored.
13 SECTION 5. This Act shall take effect on July 1, 2026.
